ss=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v47-j6v8hx-114\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v47-6p5hyh-115\"><strong>Requirements</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v47-vajka8-116\">Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v48-rgdszm-117\">Merchant must be a local MY merchants</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v48-xfwgyz-118\">Pricing</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v48-iuckbx-119\">Merchant must agree to our VA pricing below: </p><p data-block-id=\"mm751v48-amnm02-120\">i. Transaction fee: 0.5%, minimum MYR 0.5;</p><p data-block-id=\"mm751v48-dqou61-121\">ii. VA creation: RM3 / per account creation; and </p><p data-block-id=\"mm751v48-6wwz10-122\">iii. VA maintenance : RM1.5/month</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mm751v48-j35x2u-123\"><a id=\"_ujkex4eg0uw0\" display=\"false\"></a>SLA</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v48-8izwr6-124\"><strong>Entity Origin</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v48-xl8zow-125\"><strong>SLA</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v48-l03ket-126\">Local Domestic MY Merchants</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v49-8nopgz-127\">1 WD by product team</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mm751v49-15ici0-128\"><a id=\"_r0miqi6pvfyc\" display=\"false\"></a>Onboarding Flow</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v49-uvg2ue-129\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v49-0q02ne-130\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v49-ai42vj-131\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v49-dh371z-132\"><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v49-ivhdxi-133\">Channel Activation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v49-8erdkr-134\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4a-su8st9-135\">Merchant submits a request to apply for the <strong>AmBank Virtual Account</strong> payment flow via their dashboard.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4a-ewed79-136\">Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbldhwd-1dagcf-021\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4a-vwhv1t-137\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4a-q73p7m-138\">Once submitted, the request reflects in the<strong> #mo-request</strong> Slack channel and the<strong> Channel Approval and Activation </strong>section of the Admin Dashboard (AD).</p><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4a-rtjawj-139\"><br type=\"inline\"><em>Request and Spreadsheet Example via #mo-request </em>: </p><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4a-3nbop2-141\"><img data-block-id=\"mm751v4a-8ub6pz-142\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-j4cknuoj.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4a-jjk516-143\"><em>Request and Spreadsheet Example via Admin Dashboard (Channel Approval &amp; Activation) </em>: </p><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4a-xct3xf-144\"><img data-block-id=\"mm751v4a-4g8jdc-145\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-52oi8qk6.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbldhwe-mawbhn-022\"></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mm751v4a-79yap9-146\"><a id=\"_u96tqxtduroc\" display=\"false\"></a>Activation Flow</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4b-5j5o47-147\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4b-2r2rg5-148\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4b-cnlmp5-149\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4b-j6ztpd-150\"><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4b-lievid-151\">Channel Activation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4b-gwy776-152\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4b-ta6dwo-153\">MO to navigate to the<strong> Channel Approval and Activation</strong> tab in AD. <br type=\"inline\"><br type=\"inline\">Apply filter Channel and select <strong>VIRTUAL_ACCOUNT &gt; MY_AMBANK_FIXED_VA</strong> &amp; apply filter Status <strong>“NEW SUBMISSION”</strong> </p><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4c-si91zk-156\"><strong><img data-block-id=\"mm751v4c-xvv1ts-157\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-pwiztxzp.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"5\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4c-j4e7rp-158\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbldhwf-iyd08o-023\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4c-14ot5v-159\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4c-hye81y-160\">MO identifies the new submission's Business ID (BID) and clicks the View Details button.</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbldhwg-oiolzh-024\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4c-awya84-161\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4c-vbej1o-162\">MO clicks the pencil (edit) button, followed by SAVE.</p><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4d-dvdvtu-163\"><img data-block-id=\"mm751v4d-cdz52w-164\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-koy46dbh.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbldhwg-dgsb4a-025\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4d-k5o1dd-165\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4d-9q07tt-166\">MO clicks the <strong>Action</strong> button and selects <strong>Approved</strong>.<br type=\"inline\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4d-v6txvl-168\"><img data-block-id=\"mm751v4d-55grs7-169\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-gjvst449.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbldhwh-gz01mi-026\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4d-g5af9b-170\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4d-l2wma7-171\">The Virtual Account is now Live. MO can also verify activation via the <a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/b4787d82-1cc0-11ef-8834-d340ecb2f27d/Channel%20Approval/Payment%20Setting%20UI\"><u>PSS Retool</u></a> to ensure the channel is active for the merchant.</p><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4d-fi69jw-172\"><img data-block-id=\"mm751v4d-7655m3-173\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-oppt555u.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mm751v4d-iymd69-174\"><a id=\"_eo8f2o4hqql8\" display=\"false\"></a>Rejection Flow</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4e-80bo30-175\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4e-hp8otj-176\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4e-b0gii5-177\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4e-kvyxq1-178\"><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbldhwi-hy8zie-027\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4e-5png1b-179\">1.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4e-u6yele-180\">Navigate to<strong> Admin Dashboard &gt; Channel Approvals and Activations</strong>.</p><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4e-hkjudq-181\"><img data-block-id=\"mm751v4e-4gevdx-182\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-n1zsr6cs.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"3\"><p data-block-id=\"mm751v4e-rshth1-183\">MO</p></th></tr>