 product team</p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_r0miqi6pvfyc\"></a>Onboarding Flow</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Channel Activation</p></th><th><p>1</p></th><th><p>Merchant submits a request to apply for the <strong>AmBank Virtual Account</strong> payment flow via their dashboard.</p></th><th><p>Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>2</p></th><th><p>Once submitted, the request reflects in the<strong> #mo-request</strong> Slack channel and the<strong> Channel Approval and Activation </strong>section of the Admin Dashboard (AD).</p><p><br><em>Request and Spreadsheet Example via #mo-request </em>: </p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-j4cknuoj.png\"></p><p><em>Request and Spreadsheet Example via Admin Dashboard (Channel Approval &amp; Activation) </em>: </p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-52oi8qk6.png\"></p></th><th></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_u96tqxtduroc\"></a>Activation Flow</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Channel Activation</p></th><th><p>1</p></th><th><p>MO to navigate to the<strong> Channel Approval and Activation</strong> tab in AD. <br><br>Apply filter Channel and select <strong>VIRTUAL_ACCOUNT &gt; MY_AMBANK_FIXED_VA</strong> &amp; apply filter Status <strong>“NEW SUBMISSION”</strong> </p><p><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-pwiztxzp.png\"></strong></p></th><th rowspan=\"5\"><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>2</p></th><th><p>MO identifies the new submission's Business ID (BID) and clicks the View Details button.</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>3</p></th><th><p>MO clicks the pencil (edit) button, followed by SAVE.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-koy46dbh.png\"></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>4</p></th><th><p>MO clicks the <strong>Action</strong> button and selects <strong>Approved</strong>.<br></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-gjvst449.png\"></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>5</p></th><th><p>The Virtual Account is now Live. MO can also verify activation via the <a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/b4787d82-1cc0-11ef-8834-d340ecb2f27d/Channel%20Approval/Payment%20Setting%20UI\"><u>PSS Retool</u></a> to ensure the channel is active for the merchant.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-oppt555u.png\"></p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_eo8f2o4hqql8\"></a>Rejection Flow</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>1.</p></th><th><p>Navigate to<strong> Admin Dashboard &gt; Channel Approvals and Activations</strong>.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-n1zsr6cs.png\"></p></th><th rowspan=\"3\"><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>2.</p></th><th><p>Set filter to<strong> Malaysia (MY)</strong> and search by <strong>BID</strong>.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-lbrt5gga.png\"></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>3.</p></th><th><p>Click the <strong>three dots (⋮)</strong> and select <strong>Reject</strong>.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/my-va-via-ambank-image-npwbgi4f.png\"></p></th></tr></thead></table>","SeoTitle":"MY VA via Ambank","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"MY VA via Ambank","Slug":"my-va-via-ambank","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p><a id=\"_j5wih1vxvjn6\"></a>[SOP] MY Ambank VA</p><p><em>Last Update : Dec 30, 2026</em></p><p><em>MO PIC :  </em><a><em><u>Nora Atika</u></em></a></p><h1><a id=\"_49nd097njvij\"></a></h1><h1><a id=\"_ejxly55we75x\"></a>Xendit Stakeholders</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Department</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>PIC</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>PIC Role</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Partnership</p></th><th><p><a><u>Musa Sharuddin</u></a></p></th><th><p>Partnership PIC for Shopeepay</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Product</p></th><th><p><a><u>Bintoro adi Guna</u></a> </p></th><th><p>Product</p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_l0o6jdyv2txv\"></a></h1><h1><a id=\"_hbvftyg2k24s\"></a>Eligibility<br></h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Entity Type</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Eligible</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Local Domestic MY Entity Sdn Bhd / Bhd</p></th><th><p>✅</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Local Domestic MY Entity Sole Prop</p></th><th><p>✅</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Local Domestic MY Entity Association</p></th><th><p>✅</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Local Domestic MY Entity LLP / Partnership</p></th><th><p>✅</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Foreign Entity</p></th><th><p>❌</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Local / Foreign Individual</p></th><th><p>❌</p></th></tr></thead></table><p><br></p><h1><a id=\"_w2g1ajchr0f\"></a></h1><h1><a id=\"_6c0oxkffxx60\"></a>Merchant Requirements <br></h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Entity</p></th><th><p>Merchant must be a local MY merchants</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Pricing</p></th><th><p>Merchant must agree to our VA pricing below: </